# ☁ Docker Image Registries

Docker images are stored inside Image Registries.

Today I learned about the following registries:

| Registry               | Description                        |
| Docker Hub             | Public Docker Image Registry       |
| Amazon ECR             | AWS Elastic Container Registry     |
| JFrog Artifactory      | Enterprise Artifact Repository     |
| Sonatype Nexus         | Repository Manager for Docker & Other Artifacts |
| Docker Trusted Registry (DTR) | Enterprise Docker Registry |

