# 🧩 Docker Image vs Docker Container

| Docker Image | Docker Container |
|--------------|------------------|
| Read-only Template | Running Instance |
| Immutable | Read/Write Layer |
| Used to Create Containers | Executes Application |
| Can be Shared | Temporary Runtime |

